live, /health/ready)\n500: - [ ] Invocation routes registered with GET and POST\n501: - [ ] Middleware chain applied (concurrency, logging, recovery)\n502: - [ ] SessionManager interface defined\n503: - [ ] GetSandboxBySession resolves or creates sessions\n504: - [ ] createSandbox POST to Workload Manager\n505: - [ ] K8s SA token added for in-cluster auth\n506: - [ ] ReverseProxy with custom Director\n507: - [ ] Director normalizes path and injects JWT\n508: - [ ] ModifyResponse adds session header\n509: - [ ] ErrorHandler maps errors to HTTP codes\n510: - [ ] JWTManager with RSA key generation\n511: - [ ] GenerateToken with RS256, 5m expiration\n512: - [ ] TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret handles creation/loading\n513: - [ ] AlreadyExists handled for concurrent routers\n514: - [ ] concurrencyLimitMiddleware with semaphore\n515: - [ ] 429 returned when overloaded\n516: - [ ] handleHealthLive returns 200\n517: - [ ] handleHealthReady checks sessionManager\n518: - [ ] handleInvoke proxies to sandbox\n519: - [ ] Activity timestamp updated twice\n520: - [ ] Error types implement APIStatus\n521: - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL required\n522: - [ ] AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE with default\n523: - [ ] Constants defined (rsaKeySize, jwtExpiration, IdentitySecretName)\n524: - [ ] Unit tests for all components\n525: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n526: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n527: - [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n528: - [ ] No race conditions detected\n529: \n530: ---\n531: \n532: ## Files Modified/Created\n533: \n534: | File | Status | Description |\n535: |------|--------|-------------|\n536: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | Pending | Error types with APIStatus interface |\n537: | `pkg/router/errors_test.go` | Pending | Error types unit tests |\n538: | `pkg/router/config.go` | Pending | Config struct and DefaultConfig |\n539: | `pkg/router/config_test.go` | Pending | Config unit tests |\n540: | `pkg/router/store.go` | Pending | Store interface definition (or import) |\n541: | `pkg/router/logger.go` | Pending | Logger interface definition |\n542: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | Pending | JWTManager implementation |\n543: | `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Pending | JWT unit tests |\n544: | `pkg/router/session_manager.go` | Pending | SessionManager implementation |\n545: | `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` | Pending | SessionManager unit tests |\n546: | `pkg/router/middleware.go` | Pending | Concurrency, logging, recovery middleware |\n547: | `pkg/router/middleware_test.go` | Pending | Middleware unit tests |\n548: | `pkg/router/reverse_proxy.go` | Pending | Reverse proxy with Director, ModifyResponse, ErrorHandler |\n549: | `pkg/router/reverse_proxy_test.go` | Pending | Reverse proxy unit tests |\n550: | `pkg/router/handlers.go` | Pending | Health and invocation handlers |\n551: | `pkg/router/handlers_test.go` | Pending | Handlers unit tests |\n552: | `pkg/router/server.go` | Pending | HTTP Server with Gin engine |\n553: | `pkg/router/server_test.go` | Pending | Server unit tests |\n554: | `pkg/router/mocks_test.go` | Pending | Mock implementations for testing |\n555: | `pkg/router/doc.go` | Pending | Package documentation |\n556: \n557: ---\n558: \n559: ## Notes\n560: \n561: - **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n562: - **Implementation pending**\n563: - **Dependencies**:\n564:   - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` - HTTP framework\n565:   - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` - JWT signing\n566:   - `golang.org/x/net/http2` - h2c server\n567:   - `k8s.io/client-go` - Kubernetes API client\n568:   - `pkg/common/types` - SandboxInfo, CreateSandboxRequest/Response\n569: - **Environment Variables**:\n570:   - `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` (required)\n571:   - `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (optional, default \"default\")\n572: \n573: ---\n574: \n575: ## Implementation Timeline\n576: \n577: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n578: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n579: | Phase 1: Error Types & Interfaces | T1.1, T1.2 | Pending | 0% |\n580: | Phase 2: Config & Constants | T2.1-T2.3 | Pending | 0% |\n581: | Phase 3: Store Interface & Logger | T3.1, T3.2 | Pending | 0% |\n582: | Phase 4: JWTManager | T4.1-T4.6 | Pending | 0% |\n583: | Phase 5: SessionManager | T5.1-T5.5 | Pending | 0% |\n584: | Phase 6: Middleware | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n585: | Phase 7: Reverse Proxy | T7.1-T7.6 | Pending | 0% |\n586: | Phase 8: Handlers | T8.1-T8.6 | Pending | 0% |\n587: | Phase 9: Server | T9.1-T9.7 | Pending | 0% |\n588: | Phase 10: Integration Tests | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n589: | Phase 11: Mock Implementations | T11.1-T11.5 | Pending | 0% |\n590: | Phase 12: Validation & Coverage | T12.1-T12.5 | Pending | 0% |\n591: \n592: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/59 tasks)**\n\n(End of file - total 592 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Error Types & Interfaces (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Define error types in `errors.go`\n  - `SessionNotFoundError` with `SessionID` field, code `SESSION_NOT_FOUND`, HTTP 404","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775851156802,"end":1775851156824}}}}
