rHandleCodeInterpreterInvoke -v`\n\n- [x] **T8.8**: Implement `handleInvoke(c, kind)` handler\n  - Extract `namespace`, `name` from URL path params\n  - Extract `invocationPath` from wildcard param\n  - Extract `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n  - Call `sessionManager.GetSandboxBySession(ctx, sessionID, namespace, name, kind)`\n  - Check for empty `EntryPoints` → 404 `NO_ENTRY_POINT`\n  - Update activity via `storeClient.UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, time.Now())`\n  - Select entry point via `selectEntryPoint(entryPoints, invocationPath)`\n  - Build target URL via `buildTargetURL(entryPoint)`\n  - Generate JWT for `SandboxKind`/`SandboxClaimKind` only\n  - Create reverse proxy with `newReverseProxy(target, jwt, sessionID)`\n  - Serve HTTP via `proxy.ServeHTTP(c.Writer, c.Request)`\n  - Update activity again after proxy\n  - Handle errors via `handleGetSandboxError(c, err)`\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestHandleInvoke -v`\n\n- [x] **T8.9**: Implement `handleGetSandboxError(c, err)` helper\n  - Check `apierrors.IsNotFound(err)` → HTTP 404\n  - Check `apierrors.APIStatus` → use status code from APIStatus\n  - Check router `APIStatus` → use `Status()`, `Code()`, `Message()`\n  - Other errors → HTTP 500 with `\"internal server error\"`\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go build ./pkg/router/...`\n\n- [x] **T8.10**: Implement `Start(ctx)` method\n  - If `EnableTLS`: check cert/key not empty, call `ListenAndServeTLS`\n  - If not TLS: call `ListenAndServe()`\n  - Launch goroutine for `waitForShutdown(ctx)`\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServerTLSRequired -v`\n\n- [x] **T8.11**: Implement `waitForShutdown(ctx)` method\n  - Wait for `ctx.Done()`\n  - Create shutdown context with 10s timeout\n  - Call `httpServer.Shutdown(shutdownCtx)`\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServerGracefulShutdown -v`\n\n- [x] **T8.12**: Implement `Stop()` method\n  - Create context with 10s timeout\n  - Call `httpServer.Shutdown(ctx)`\n  - Return error\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServerStop -v`\n\n- [x] **T8.13**: Implement `GetEngine()` method\n  - Return `*gin.Engine` for testing access\n  - File: `pkg/router/server.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServerGetEngine -v`\n\n### Phase 9: Mock Implementations for Testing (ST-9)\n\n- [x] **T9.1**: Implement `MockStore` in test files\n  - `GetSandboxBySessionIDFunc func(ctx, sessionID) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)`\n  - `StoreSandboxFunc func(ctx, sandbox) error`\n  - `UpdateSessionLastActivityFunc func(ctx, sessionID, at) error`\n  - File: `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestMockStore -v`\n\n- [x] **T9.2**: Implement `MockLogger` in test files\n  - `InfoCalls []string`\n  - `ErrorCalls []string`\n  - `WarningCalls []string`\n  - Methods record calls for verification\n  - File: `pkg/router/middleware_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestMockLogger -v`\n\n- [x] **T9.3**: Implement `mockSessionManager` in test files\n  - `getFunc func(ctx, sessionID, namespace, name, kind) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)`\n  - Implements `SessionManager` interface\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestMockSessionManager -v`\n\n- [x] **T9.4**: Implement `MockHTTPClient` in test files\n  - `DoFunc func(req) (*http.Response, error)`\n  - File: `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go build ./pkg/router/...`\n\n### Phase 10: Validation & Coverage (ST-10)\n\n- [x] **T10.1**: All unit tests pass\n  - `go test ./pkg/router -v`\n  - File: `pkg/router/*_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.2**: Verify error type tests pass\n  - `SessionNotFoundError`, `SandboxUnreachableError`, etc.\n  - File: `pkg/router/errors_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestError -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.3**: Verify config tests pass\n  - `DefaultConfig`, nil config handling\n  - File: `pkg/router/config_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestConfig -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.4**: Verify JWT tests pass\n  - Token generation, expiration, PEM encoding\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTManager -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.5**: Verify session manager tests pass\n  - NewSessionManager, GetSandboxBySession, createSandbox\n  - File: `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestSessionManager -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.6**: Verify middleware tests pass\n  - Concurrency limit, logging, recovery\n  - File: `pkg/router/middleware_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestMiddleware -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.7**: Verify reverse proxy tests pass\n  - selectEntryPoint, buildTargetURL\n  - File: `pkg/router/reverse_proxy_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestReverseProxy -v`\n\n- [x] **T10.8**: Verify server tests pass\n  - NewServer, health handlers, routes, shutdown\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServer -v`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 ──── T1.2\n  │\n  ▼\nT2.1 ──── T2.2 ──── T2.3\n  │\n  ▼\nT3.1 ──── T3.2 ──── T3.3 ──── T3.4\n  │\n  ▼\nT4.1 ──── T4.2 ──── T4.3 ──── T4.4 ──── T4.5 ──── T4.6\n  │\n  ▼\nT5.1 ──── T5.2 ──── T5.3 ──── T5.4 ──── T5.5\n  │\n  ▼\nT6.1 ──── T6.2 ──── T6.3 ──── T6.4\n  │\n  ▼\nT7.1 ──── T7.2 ──── T7.3 ──── T7.4 ──── T7.5 ──── T7.6 ──── T7.7\n  │\n  ▼\nT8.1 ──── T8.2 ──── T8.3 ──── T8.4 ──── T8.5 ──── T8.6 ──── T8.7 ──── T8.8 ──── T8.9 ──── T8.10 ──── T8.11 ──── T8.12 ──── T8.13\n  │\n  ▼\nT9.1 ──── T9.2 ──── T9.3 ──── T9.4\n  │\n  ▼\nT10.1 ──── T10.2 ──── T10.3 ──── T10.4 ──── T10.5 ──── T10.6 ──── T10.7 ──── T10.8\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| All router tests | `go test ./pkg/router -v` |\n| Error types tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestError -v` |\n| Config tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestConfig -v` |\n| JWT tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTManager -v` |\n| Session manager tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestSessionManager -v` |\n| Middleware tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestMiddleware -v` |\n| Reverse proxy tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestReverseProxy -v` |\n| Server tests | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestServer -v` |\n| Build verification | `go build ./pkg/router/...` |\n| Package vet | `go vet ./pkg/router/...` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [x] Server struct defined with all required fields\n- [x] Config struct with Port, TLS, MaxConcurrentRequests, Debug\n- [x] NewServer constructor initializes Gin engine\n- [x] Gin mode set based on Debug config\n- [x] Server.Start supports TLS and non-TLS\n- [x] Graceful shutdown with 10s deadline\n- [x] Health routes registered (/health/live, /health/ready)\n- [x] Invocation routes registered with GET and POST\n- [x] Middleware chain applied (concurrency, logging, recovery)\n- [x] SessionManager interface defined\n- [x] GetSandboxBySession resolves or creates sessions\n- [x] createSandbox POST to Workload Manager\n- [x] K8s SA token added for in-cluster auth\n- [x] ReverseProxyWrapper with Director, ModifyResponse, ErrorHandler\n- [x] Director normalizes path and injects JWT\n- [x] ModifyResponse adds session header\n- [x] ErrorHandler maps errors to HTTP codes (502/504)\n- [x] JWTManager with RSA key generation\n- [x] GenerateToken with RS256, 5m expiration\n- [x] TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret placeholder\n- [x] concurrencyLimitMiddleware with semaphore\n- [x] 429 returned when overloaded\n- [x] handleHealthLive returns 200 {\"status\":\"alive\"}\n- [x] handleHealthReady checks sessionManager availability\n- [x] handleInvoke proxies to sandbox with activity tracking\n- [x] Activity timestamp updated before and after proxy\n- [x] Error types implement APIStatus interface\n- [x] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL required for SessionManager\n- [x] AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE with default \"default\"\n- [x] Constants defined (rsaKeySize, jwtExpiration, IdentitySecretName)\n- [x] Unit tests for all components\n- [x] Mock implementations for testing\n\n---\n\n## Files Modified/Created\n\n| File | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router/errors.go` | Created | Error types with APIStatus interface |\n| `pkg/router/errors_test.go` | Created | Error types unit tests |\n| `pkg/router/config.go` | Created | Config struct and DefaultConfig |\n| `pkg/router/config_test.go` | Created | Config unit tests |\n| `pkg/router/doc.go` | Created | Interface definitions (Store, Logger, SessionManager, APIStatus) |\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | Created | JWTManager implementation with RS256 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Created | JWT unit tests |\n| `pkg/router/session_manager.go` | Created | SessionManager implementation |\n| `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` | Created | SessionManager unit tests with MockStore |\n| `pkg/router/middleware.go` | Created | Concurrency, logging, recovery middleware |\n| `pkg/router/middleware_test.go` | Created | Middleware unit tests with MockLogger |\n| `pkg/router/reverse_proxy.go` | Created | Reverse proxy with Director, ModifyResponse, ErrorHandler |\n| `pkg/router/reverse_proxy_test.go` | Created | Reverse proxy unit tests |\n| `pkg/router/server.go` | Created | HTTP Server with Gin engine, handlers, shutdown |\n| `pkg/router/server_test.go` | Created | Server unit tests with mockSessionManager |\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n- **Implementation completed**\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` - HTTP framework\n  - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` - JWT signing\n  - `golang.org/x/net/http2` - HTTP/2 transport\n  - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` - APIStatus interface\n  